FREEPBX_WEB_SERVER_PAGE: Configure FreePBX web administration service access ports
FREEPBX_HTTP_PORT_DESC: The HTTP port for the web server. Defaults to 8070.
FREEPBX_HTTPS_PORT_DESC: The secure HTTP port for the web server. Defaults to 8071.
FREEPBX_PBX_SERVER_PAGE: Configure Asterisk PBX server communication ports
FREEPVX_PJSIP_PORT_DESC: The PJSIP transport port for the Asterisk PBX server. Defaults to 5060.
FREEPVX_SIP_PORT_DESC: The SIP transport port for the Asterisk PBX server. Defaults to 5160.
